title: The DC Check-In With Dominick Cruz
author: Daniel Cormier
description:
I spoke with Dominic Cruz today after the comments he made at media day.  We sat down and had a honest conversation about our opinions amongst other things. Also a little about his fight. We also got joined by the special ref Micheal BISPING lol. Was fun and good to sit with em!
